<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Fort_charles_1920.jpg" class="image" title="Fort charles 1920.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Fort_charles_1920.jpg/130px-Fort_charles_1920.jpg" width="130" height="197" border="0" /></a><br />
